import React from "react"; export const About = () => (

About me...

I am a dedicated, versatile and detail oriented Full Stack developer. Finished different freeCodeCamp's courses and obtained several certificates, being the Legacy Full Stack Certificate the last one. Since last year I have been creating different types of interactive applications using Javascript as the main language and some tools from it's echosystem. I am passionate about creating new and useful applications and making them the most efficient they can be, and I am excited to work in a team and learn new things.
